            "title": "General Motors Non-GAAP EPS of $2.51 beats by $0.25, revenue of $45.29B misses by $750M",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>General Motors <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20376776-gm-releases-2025-financial-results-and-2026-guidance-board-declares-dividend-at-20-percent\">press release</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GM\" title=\"General Motors Company\">GM</a></span>): Q4 Non-GAAP EPS of $2.51 <span> beats by $0.25</span>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $45.29B (-5.1% Y/Y) <span> misses by $750M</span>.</li>\n<li><div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<span class=\"sa-table-scroll-wrapper sa-hide-scrollbar\"><span data-intersection-boundary=\"start\" data-test-id=\"table-scroll-wrapper-boundary-start\"></span><div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<span class=\"sa-table-scroll-wrapper sa-hide-scrollbar\"><span data-intersection-boundary=\"start\" data-test-id=\"table-scroll-wrapper-boundary-start\"></span><table data-should-enlarge=\"true\"><tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 203.588px;\"><p data-eci=\"true\">Final 2025 Guidance</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 131.84px;\"> </td>\n<td style=\"width: 77.7315px;\"><p>2025 Results</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 235.486px;\"><p>2026 Guidance</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 203.588px;\"><p>Net income attributable to stockholders</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 131.84px;\"><p>$7.7 billion - $8.3 billion</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 77.7315px;\"><p>$2.7 billion</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 235.486px;\"><p>$10.3 billion - $11.7 billion vs $11.83 consensus</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 203.588px;\"><p>EBIT-adjusted</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 131.84px;\"><p>$12.0 billion - $13.0 billion</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 77.7315px;\"><p>$12.7 billion</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 235.486px;\"><p>$13.0 billion - $15.0 billion</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 203.588px;\"><p>Automotive operating cash flow</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 131.84px;\"><p>$19.2 billion - $21.2 billion</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 77.7315px;\"><p>$18.7 billion</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 235.486px;\"><p>$19.0 billion - $23.0 billion</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 203.588px;\"><p>Adjusted automotive free cash flow</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 131.84px;\"><p>$10.0 billion - $11.0 billion</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 77.7315px;\"><p>$10.6 billion</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 235.486px;\"><p>$9.0 billion - $11.0 billion</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 203.588px;\"><p>EPS-diluted</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 131.84px;\"><p>$8.30 - $9.05</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 77.7315px;\"><p>$3.27</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 235.486px;\"><p>$11.00 - $13.00</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 203.588px;\"><p>EPS-diluted-adjusted</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 131.84px;\"><p>$9.75 - $10.50</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 77.7315px;\"><p>$10.60</p></td>\n<td style=\"width: 235.486px;\"><p>$11.00 - $13.00</p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<span data-intersection-boundary=\"end\" data-test-id=\"table-scroll-wrapper-boundary-end\"></span></span><button class=\"sa-table-enlarge-button\" type=\"button\">Click to enlarge</button>\n</div>\n<span data-intersection-boundary=\"end\" data-test-id=\"table-scroll-wrapper-boundary-end\"></span></span><button class=\"sa-table-enlarge-button\" type=\"button\">Click to enlarge</button>\n</div></li>\n<li>Shares <span>-2%</span> PM.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
