            "id": "4542747",
            "title": "Quant check on health insurers amid Trump admin's proposal for nearly flat Medicare payment rates",
            "description": "<html><body><p data-eci=\"true\"> </p>\n<p>Shares of major U.S. health insurers fell sharply after the Trump administration proposed holding Medicare Advantage payment rates nearly<em> </em>flat for 2027—sending stocks lower as investors were broadly expecting an increase.</p>\n<p>The Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services proposed an average<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4542683-humana-other-insurers-fall-on-flat-rates-for-medicaid-advantage-payments-in-2027\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" increase to Medicare Advantage payments of just 0.09% \"> increase to Medicare Advantage payments of just 0.09% </a>for plan year 2027—far below the<strong> </strong>4-6% rise analysts had expected. This figure would amount to roughly $700M in additional payments industry-wide.</p>\n<p>Health insurance stocks are sensitive to government reimbursement policy, as Medicare Advantage is a core business segment for companies like UnitedHealth (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UNH\" title=\"UnitedHealth Group Incorporated\">UNH</a>) and Humana (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HUM\" title=\"Humana Inc.\">HUM</a>).</p>\n<p><span>With a shift in sentiment translating at the stock level, Quant ratings provide a snapshot of which managed healthcare provider names are screening strongest:</span></p>\n<p data-id=\"77bf7a73-1377-4746-a6f0-d60e32efe7f2\"><span data-ai=\"\">Here is the list:</span></p>\n<ol data-id=\"60ca1889-29c5-4a67-95bc-9dd68f09fd37\">\n<li data-id=\"02afdf67-a7f3-49a7-b30b-61132b845c10\"><p data-id=\"87c8b581-8459-463d-b49f-ae80f50bf028\"><span data-ai=\"\">HealthEquity (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HQY\" title=\"HealthEquity, Inc.\">HQY</a>), Quant Rating: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HQY/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.70\">3.70</a> </span></p></li>\n<li data-id=\"aac760cb-f11d-4edb-b2c2-40a810e8c0a4\"><p data-id=\"d1c05ed4-e062-4a61-ab2f-717ae5b26650\"><span data-ai=\"\">Centene Corporation (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CNC\" title=\"Centene Corporation\">CNC</a>), Quant Rating: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CNC/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.47\">3.47</a></span><span data-ai=\"\"></span><span data-ai=\"\"> (down 4.7% pre-market on Tuesday)</span></p></li>\n<li data-id=\"aac760cb-f11d-4edb-b2c2-40a810e8c0a4\"><p data-id=\"d1c05ed4-e062-4a61-ab2f-717ae5b26650\"><span data-ai=\"\">Alignment Healthcare (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ALHC\" title=\"Alignment Healthcare, Inc.\">ALHC</a>), Quant Rating: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ALHC/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.42\">3.42 </a></span><span data-ai=\"\">(down 13.9% pre-market on Tuesday)</span></p></li>\n<li data-id=\"a61b088d-1c40-49bc-8018-2a5b99344880\"><p data-id=\"61a5dccb-b541-42ea-9494-e61daac3042b\"><span data-ai=\"\">UnitedHealth Group (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UNH\" title=\"UnitedHealth Group Incorporated\">UNH</a>) , Quant Rating: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UNH/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.32\">3.32</a></span><span data-ai=\"\"> (down 8.6% pre-market on Tuesday)</span></p></li>\n<li data-id=\"f656e104-c252-4dc2-a60d-489da9d0de66\"><p data-id=\"01309a9a-a58c-4e5a-a185-ac515247ecd8\">Progyny (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PGNY\" title=\"Progyny, Inc.\">PGNY</a>), Quant Rating: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PGNY/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.25\">3.25</a></p></li>\n<li data-id=\"d26bc8b4-d326-4902-8463-a0af9e886aa9\"><p data-id=\"17896cb0-e62b-4063-b591-56f66ddafe77\">Elevance Health (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ELV\" title=\"Elevance Health, Inc.\">ELV</a>), Quant Rating: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ELV/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.11\">3.13</a> <span data-ai=\"\">(down 6.9% pre-market on Tuesday)</span></p></li>\n<li data-id=\"c654d3af-550e-437b-a78a-554e73af206a\"><p data-id=\"096e34ba-7aef-4eaf-a463-4f760cd0b01e\"><span data-ai=\"\">Humana (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HUM\" title=\"Humana Inc.\">HUM</a>), Quant Rating: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HUM/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.11\">3.11</a></span><span data-ai=\"\"> (down 13.9% pre-market on Tuesday)</span></p></li>\n<li data-id=\"4b569a3e-a753-4f8b-8831-948f57676553\"><p data-id=\"89b3b8e1-b70f-4fc4-b059-470c1fad4a70\"><span data-ai=\"\">Molina Healthcare (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MOH\" title=\"Molina Healthcare, Inc.\">MOH</a>), Quant Rating: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MOH/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"2.81\">2.81</a></span><span data-ai=\"\"> (down 3.7% pre-market on Tuesday)</span></p></li>\n</ol>\n<p><span data-ai=\"\">ETFs to track: (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IXJ\" title=\"iShares Global Healthcare ETF\">IXJ</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VHT\" title=\"Vanguard Health Care Index Fund ETF Shares\">VHT</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XBI\" title=\"SPDR® S&amp;P Biotech ETF\">XBI</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XLV\" title=\"The Health Care Select Sector SPDR® Fund ETF\">XLV</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RSPH\" title=\"Invesco S&amp;P 500® Equal Weight Health Care ETF\">RSPH</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KIE\" title=\"SPDR® S&amp;P Insurance ETF\">KIE</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IAK\" title=\"iShares U.S. Insurance ETF\">IAK</a>).</span></p>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
