            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>UPS <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20376742-ups-releases-4q-2025-earnings-and-provides-2026-guidance\">press release</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UPS\" title=\"United Parcel Service, Inc.\">UPS</a></span>): Q4 Non-GAAP EPS of $2.38 <span> beats by $0.18</span>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $24.5B (-3.2% Y/Y) <span> beats by $490M</span>.</li>\n<li>\n<p data-eci=\"true\">For the full year 2026, on a consolidated basis, UPS expects revenue to be approximately $89.7 billion and non-GAAP adjusted operating margin to be approximately 9.6%.</p>\n<p>The company is planning capital expenditures of about $3.0 billion and dividend payments of around $5.4 billion, subject to board approval. The effective tax rate is expected to be approximately 23.0%.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
